      <title>拜耳在美国佐治亚州以20亿美元的汇总判决命中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/bayer-hit-with-2-billion-roundup-verdict-in-us-state-of-georgia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜耳（Bayer AG）在美国佐治亚州的陪审团下令向原告支付约21亿美元的费用，该原告声称其综述性杂草造成了癌症，这是诉讼中的最新挫折，已经使这家德国公司损失了约100亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/bayer-hit-with-2-billion-roundup-verdict-in-us-state-of-georgia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 09:49:05 GMT</pubDate>
