    <item>
      <title>穆迪（Moody）确认在A2的波兰评级，称赞防御支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/moody-s-affirms-polish-rating-at-a2-praises-defense-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪的收视率肯定了波兰在A2的长期外国发行人的评级，并表示其动态经济和解锁的欧盟资金减轻了预算资产负债表的恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/moody-s-affirms-polish-rating-at-a2-praises-defense-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 09:21:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>激进主义者对冲基金变成猎物，因为西班牙媒体的战斗爆发了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/activist-hedge-fund-turns-prey-as-spanish-media-fight-flares-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[十年前的股东活动主义运动之后，琥珀资本创始人约瑟夫·奥尔利安（Joseph Oughourlian）赢得了西班牙最有影响力的媒体集团的控制权。现在，他是罢工的人。]]></description>
