      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希思罗机场说，停电关闭后，它已经完全运行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/london-heathrow-airport-lhr-closed-due-to-power-outage-caused-by-fire-m8jusd2c</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦希思罗机场（Heathrow Airport）表示，在史无前例的日停电后，它是开放和全部运营的，这使旅行在欧洲最繁忙的机场中待了数十万乘客。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/london-heathrow-airport-lhr-closed-due-to-power-outage-caused-by-fire-m8jusd2c</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 06:45:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希思罗机场停电暴露了机场电源中的弱点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/heathrow-blackout-exposes-weak-spot-in-airport-s-power-supplies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦希思罗机场（London Heathrow）在周五的前所未有的停电使该机场对潜在脆弱的基础设施的依赖焦点，而英国最大的枢纽正在游说雄心勃勃的扩张计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/heathrow-blackout-exposes-weak-spot-in-airport-s-power-supplies</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
